Title: Two Steps
DateModified: '2019-02-27'
DatePublished: '2019-02-27'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/two-steps
SetInCountry: India
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Syed Danish Arafat
AuthorCountry: India
Text: 'In this story, I''m gonna write about of two best friends who loved a same
  girl.

  The girl is belongs to a Middle class family and she can''t afford anything expensive.
  And she wants to be a Doctor somehow their parents collected some money to sent
  her foreign to continue her studies and complete her goal.

  The two bestfriends discussed and fixed, first of all we goes to the same college
  and study with her. If she really intrested in us then she has to choose. Both friends
  are belongs to a rich family and they live a luxurious life, everygirl died on their
  looks and everyone wants a luxurious life.

  But she is not anymore interested in this life, she wants to live a normal life.
  Everyone try to convince the boys but, they only saying about the middle class girl.
  Whenever, One of both proposed her, she rejected and said I''m not all intrested
  on these, I wants to travel the world, I wants to help poor peoples, a hospital
  to free checkup.one of the boy is trying normaly, but the another one is loving
  her from his soul.

  Her words flagged on his heart and he donated her eyes to a needy person.

  When his friends saw him in this condition, he said to the middle class girl. The
  girl came......... "AND EVERYTHING IS SUSPENSE".'
